Package com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin

Class AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin.AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BugTrackerPlugin, ChangesetDiscoveryPlugin
    @Deprecated
public abstract class AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements BugTrackerPlugin, ChangesetDiscoveryPlugin
    Deprecated.
    Instead of implementing this interface, plugin can calculate candidate changesets before filing the bug using fields in BugSubmission.getIssueDetail(), namely getLastBuildWithoutIssue(), getFileName() and getDetectedInBuild()
    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing both BugTrackerPlugin and ChangesetDiscoveryPlugin would extend.
